QuestData.Title: Enough is Ookin' Enough
QuestData.Description: Virmen, they bite too much.$b$bThey bite Mung-Mung's carrot. They bite Mung-Mung's pumpkin. Mung-Mung try to shoo them away, and the dookers bite Mung-Mung's tail and foot.$b$bEnough is ookin' enough.$b$bYou fight way better than Mung-Mung does. Bring back their bitey teeth. Then we see who does the biting.
QuestData.CompletionText: You bring back those teeth, and maybe Mung-Mung will have some hops for you.
QuestData.RewardText: So many teeth! Maybe Mung-Mung will glue them together to make a tiny rake.
